de.oaam.model.oaam.allocations

Interface SubconnectionAssignment

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ModeDependentElementA, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, OaamBaseElementA, VariantDependentElementA
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SubconnectionAssignmentImpl

    public interface SubconnectionAssignment
extends OaamBaseElementA, VariantDependentElementA, ModeDependentElementA
    A representation of the model object 'Subconnection Assignment'. A allocations of a subconnection to a device or subdevice.

    The following features are supported:

    • Capability
    • Subconnection
    • Target Device
    See Also:
    AllocationsPackage.getSubconnectionAssignment()
